{u'poster_path': u'/k2C2Aq0BxmUBwLPHkOMbs7FVmNZ.jpg', u'title': u'Promise Me This', u'overview': u"Promise Me This is a film written and directed by the award-winning Serbian filmmaker Emir Kusturica. An old man named \u017divojin Markovi\u0107, living in a remote village prays for his grandson Tsane to go to the city, sell his cow and bring back a wife. In the city he is supposed to meet up with his grandfather's stepbrother, but this man is dead. Instead, he meets this man's two grandsons, two good-natured brothers who are nevertheless small-time criminals and experts in demolition. Tsane soon clicks with these men, and also falls in love with a schoolgirl (Jasna), who he wants to marry as part of his testament with his grandfather. He gets involved in this girl's family affairs, rescuing both her and her mother from prostitution and gangsters headed by a man called Bajo, and the new group of people return to the small village in time to celebrate \u017divojin's wedding to his neighbor, despite the gangsters' best efforts to stop the celebration, which results in a double wedding .", u'release_date': u'2007-05-26', u'popularity': 0.199523, u'original_title': u'Zavet', u'backdrop_path': u'/s89pu5fIb88la8rLLTwL2Grymtq.jpg', u'vote_count': 6, u'video': False, u'adult': False, u'vote_average': 6.1, u'genre_ids': [35, 18], u'id': 8269, u'original_language': u'en'}